  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Pulpit Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 2.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "The strangers",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". These are plainly called in the Septuagint \"proselytes\" (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "τοὺς",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "προσηλὺτους",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). They were, of course, foreign workmen, who came in pursuit of their trade. The injunctions as to \"strangers,\" and with regard to showing them kindness, are very numerous, beginning with ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 12:19, 48, 49",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 22:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(20); Exodus 23:9; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 19:10, 33, 34",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; Numbers 15:14-16; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 10:18, 19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 8:33-35",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
